不得抗告。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　103　　 年　　1　　 月　　13　　日\r\n　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　書記官　吳旻玲","type":"裁定","historyHash":"5d66d8aacde13bb1282944ed","mainText":"","opinion":"","relatedIssues":[{"lawName":"民事訴訟法","issueRef":"173"},{"lawName":"民事訴訟法","issueRef":"196 2"},{"lawName":"民事訴訟法","issueRef":"268"},{"lawName":"民事訴訟法","issueRef":"268-2"},{"lawName":"民事訴訟法","issueRef":"276"},{"lawName":"證券交易法","issueRef":"20 2"}],"party":[]}
